，萊塔尼亞的詩集......是叫《兩個月亮與金盞花》？", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_215_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  您的萊塔尼亞語一向很好。", "name": "燭騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_215_1#1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_215_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  哈哈，只是必要的外交學習。我猜您喜歡金盞花？今天的卡西米爾已經很少有人懂得欣賞詩歌了。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1#6"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_215_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1#6", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......字符終歸脫離不了想像，這些都只是想像的符號。", "name": "燭騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_215_1#1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  對當代人而言，詩歌不過是毫無美感的文字迷宮，自作多情，矯揉造作。", "name": "燭騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_215_1#1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  也許卡西米爾人已經習慣於別樣的消費，而詩歌總是與這類消費無緣，這很正常。", "name": "燭騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_215_1#1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_215_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......您似乎別有所指？", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_215_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  只是談論詩歌，麥基先生。", "name": "燭騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_215_1#2"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_215_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  您應該還有些話要對我們說吧，女士？", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_215_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  唔......是什麼呢。", "name": "燭騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_215_1#1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  啊，您的新眼鏡很適合您，麥基先生。", "name": "燭騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_215_1#1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_215_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  哈哈......您、您居然能注意到這種事，真讓人意外，哈哈......", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1#3"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_215_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  咳，不過，您該說的不是這個，先前在城際網路和紙媒上出現的一些謠言......", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_215_1#3", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  啊......紅酒浴池？", "name": "燭騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_215_1#3"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_215_1#3", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  是的，那是對您聲譽的詆毀......", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_215_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  真的會有人用紅酒泡澡嗎？不會黏答答的嗎？", "name": "燭騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_215_1#1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_215_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  呃？大概......我不知道。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1#3"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_215_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  呵......這種新聞又有誰會信呢？", "name": "燭騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_215_1#1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_215_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  有人會信的，德羅斯特女士......會有很多人信的。哪怕他們知道真相未必如此，他們也願意摻和這些事情。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_215_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  事後澄清一下不就行了？", "name": "燭騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_215_1#1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_215_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  唉，女士，您總是把騎士之外的事情想得太簡單了......", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1#2"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_215_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我已經聯絡了玫瑰新聞報業的總部，這是某家娛樂報刊的編輯私人所為。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  似乎在發現的時候已經引起了不小的反響，出於各種考量沒有立刻撤回......", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_215_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這是他們的工作方式，我不怪他們。", "name": "燭騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_215_1#1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_215_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  您很寬容，但這更讓我為您感到委屈。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1#2"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  您把幾乎所有私人收入都捐贈給了萊塔尼亞的貧困地區，為家鄉修建學校，建設移動平台。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1#2"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_215_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  但就算現在闢謠，經歷過狂歡的群眾也不會去在意真相如何。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  傷害和詆毀是很簡單的，他們會把這些謠言和噱頭握在手上，奔相走告。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  可您幾時見過，真相揭露以後，這些曾經傷害過您的人會去幫您洗清冤屈，澄清事實的？", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_215_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這些八卦能讓人們感到新鮮刺激，澄清事實卻是一件無聊的事情，這也是理所當然的。", "name": "燭騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_215_1#2"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_215_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  唉，您怎麼這麼無所謂呢！", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1#2"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  您這樣清正廉直的騎士應該成為其他人的榜樣！這本該讓您有更好的名聲，而且——", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1#2"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_215_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  麥基。", "name": "燭騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_215_1#6"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_215_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  呃......", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1#3"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_215_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我很感動。", "name": "燭騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_215_1#1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  您是個多愁善感的人......也是個溫柔的人。", "name": "燭騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_215_1#1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_215_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1#2"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_215_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......作為聯合會發言人，保證各位騎士不受場外因素干擾，也是我應該做的。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  只是，請您多在乎一下自己的生活。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_215_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  啊......對了。", "name": "燭騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_215_1#1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  決鬥賽的賽程表什麼時候發佈？", "name": "燭騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_215_1#1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_215_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  唉......您怎麼連自己的比賽都不上心呢？", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  如果不出意外，您的下一個對手是灰須騎士，之後是......耀騎士。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_215_1#3", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......", "name": "燭騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_215_1#3"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_215_1#3", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......您很吃驚嗎，女士？", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1#3"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_215_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  當然。耀騎士，瑪嘉烈·臨光......這個名字我聽過很多次了，很美，剛強，又優雅。", "name": "燭騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_215_1#2"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_215_